263
00:14:50,890 --> 00:14:52,016
Relax.

264
00:14:53,726 --> 00:14:54,560
What did he say?

265
00:14:55,144 --> 00:14:57,271
-That you're better than your father.
-Hey!

266
00:14:57,354 --> 00:14:58,480
I mean,

267
00:14:58,564 --> 00:15:00,858
that's what my father said.

268
00:15:01,984 --> 00:15:02,985
Fine.

269
00:15:03,152 --> 00:15:06,405
-It's like you're going to bite me.
-Don't be dramatic.

270
00:15:06,989 --> 00:15:08,157
Dramatic?

271
00:15:08,824 --> 00:15:10,701
Let's not do this to each other.

272
00:15:11,201 --> 00:15:14,622
We're cousins.
We should be friendly to each other.

273
00:15:14,705 --> 00:15:18,000
And our objectives are different in scale.

274
00:15:18,250 --> 00:15:19,793
I didn't say anything.

275
00:15:23,839 --> 00:15:24,673
Let's just go eat.

276
00:15:33,223 --> 00:15:34,350
DREAMS

277
00:15:35,142 --> 00:15:36,143
