381
00:21:22,656 --> 00:21:23,699
Here I go.

382
00:21:23,949 --> 00:21:25,117
All right.

383
00:21:29,037 --> 00:21:29,871
Are you okay?

384
00:21:30,664 --> 00:21:32,207
Are you hurt? Let me see.

385
00:21:33,333 --> 00:21:34,668
I knew this would happen.

386
00:21:35,294 --> 00:21:36,461
Let's stop for today.

387
00:21:36,628 --> 00:21:39,006
You're hurt, so don't pay me
for today's lesson.

388
00:21:39,381 --> 00:21:42,467
Come on. It was my fault.
I still need to pay you.

389
00:21:43,176 --> 00:21:46,346
I see you are sensible
the more I get to know you.

390
00:21:46,430 --> 00:21:47,764
You're cool, too.

391
00:21:47,848 --> 00:21:49,474
-You know that?
-Goodness.

392
00:21:49,558 --> 00:21:50,934
Why are you so enthusiastic?

393
00:21:51,101 --> 00:21:52,227
I'm not.

394
00:21:52,311 --> 00:21:55,605
It's true that all of my students
like baseball.

395
00:21:55,814 --> 00:21:58,400
