often and consistently like you.

396
00:21:58,483 --> 00:22:00,694
-You don't even spare yourself.
-You see,

397
00:22:02,446 --> 00:22:03,572
I might grow to like it

398
00:22:03,822 --> 00:22:06,366
-if I do this.
-Like what? Baseball?

399
00:22:06,450 --> 00:22:07,451
Well,

400
00:22:07,909 --> 00:22:10,037
-something similar.
-Softball?

401
00:22:10,287 --> 00:22:11,913
Gosh, I won't pay.

402
00:22:14,291 --> 00:22:17,461
Jae-hee, about the data
sent by the strategy analysis team...

403
00:22:24,134 --> 00:22:25,218
Why are you laughing?

404
00:22:25,302 --> 00:22:27,471
Do you feel his absence?

405
00:22:27,554 --> 00:22:28,805
No.

406
00:22:29,264 --> 00:22:32,142
-He knows how to earn his keep.
-Look at you.

407
00:22:32,434 --> 00:22:34,394
You gave him a hard time
for his connections.

408
00:22:34,478 --> 00:22:35,479
Is he helpful now?

409
00:22:38,607 --> 00:22:40,067
Connections...

